The component boundaries will follow the established layered structure with some enhancements for the complex domain:

**Component Design:**
- **API Layer (app/api/)** — REST endpoints, request validation, OpenAPI specs
- **Service Layer (app/services/)** — Business logic, complex workflows, external integrations
- **Model Layer (app/models/)** — SQLAlchemy entities, relationships, data constraints
- **Schema Layer (app/schemas/)** — Pydantic DTOs, request/response validation
- **Core Layer (app/core/)** — Configuration, database sessions, security utilities
- **Utils Layer (app/utils/)** — Cross-cutting utilities, encryption, audit helpers

